How do we hack someones privacy? [Brainstorming]
-malicious virus or worm
-replaying cookies to get into password protected accounts
-using scripts to "crack" a password
-using a insecure network to collect information
-adding a computer to a botnet
What aproach does Kevin Mitnick describe for getting personally identifiable information?
-Mitnick is describing using the "The art of deception" to take personal information, instead of heacking with scipts he takes advantage of social engineering to gain the infromation they want.
